{"tid":790411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡冠深批陳浩天去信美國要求撤銷中港世貿身份不恰當","createTime":"2018-08-23T03:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T04:10:24.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6680283055fc55bf13801b7f349c0828797ae2","tid":790411,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:46:36.000Z","msg":"你條撚樣幾個月前話只有大灣區人喎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414051-20180823.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414051-20180823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h7c0o%2BmwdMUlfomTdpq4wcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3cd18eb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414051-20180823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d0863820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414051-20180823.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨陳浩天早前向美國總統特朗普發出公開信，要求撤銷香港及中國的世貿組織身份，香港中華總商會會長蔡冠深批評有關行為不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n蔡冠深指，香港是自由經濟體，如果在世貿組織中身分有動搖，會對香港不利。<br />\n<br />\n對於中美貿易戰的發展，蔡冠深希望中美關係緩和，他指香港經濟現時受內地影響，因此要爭取拓展新興市場，不能依賴單一市場。"},{"pid":"4e5bc0a5943eb0ae0e69369c70fc9f4f63b06a13","tid":790411,"uid":17859,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意大灣區<br />\n宜家如你所願 加快融合又唔肯<br />\n即係點呀愛蟈畜生"},{"pid":"877a7ea4abfb7110f995adcf254fa5dff636d1f7","tid":790411,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"威啦，總商會都反對離獨立又近一步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2f41f04f792c24d96c1d82cf76488ce3835d94","tid":790411,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"真.死穴已試出"},{"pid":"7312b64fc1a20089eefa12d06cbdce95b904d5fb","tid":790411,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:52:03.000Z","msg":"共赴「國」難啦<br />\n<br />\